name: Cartuchito
overview: This hack is a fictional story about Mr. Wilson and Ronaldo, who are the brazilian Game Grumps. They arrive to a sweet kingdom dominated by a evil pudding that wishes to be the most famous and powerful of the world. By that, he kidnaps a little (electric) guitar and the most important cartridge of the kingdom. The "Cartuchito". Mr. Wilson and Ronaldo decide that it's their job to save their friend and take the power from the evil king's hands.
